Joe Keaton https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joe_Keaton 0 Joseph Hallie Keaton (July 6, 1867 – January 13, 1946) was an American vaudeville performer and silent film actor. He was the father of actor Buster Keaton and appeared with his son in several of his films.
